snippet.title: The Door VR - Launch Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
A locked laboratory, tricks hidden in it,
And only one exit that you can break out of the lab...
Escape from the lab by finding the hidden hints!
It is up to you which ending you will be facing with.
New release for Playstation 4 on September 21th, 2018!
The game presents the overwhelming sense of immersion as supporting PS VR.    

http://facebook.com/skonecvr

Rated Mature:  Intense Violence, Blood and Gore, Partial Nudity, Language
